channel.description:
Okay I release Project Lmao Scape V1 it was kinda crappy no one liked it but now im release Project Lmao Scape V1.5 and the difference in the 2 are this one the shops are moved all new items are added in item.cfg file i add all the good pvp armour besides that one stuff and they all equip rite i got the good claws model and ints and all specs work some are kinda high and some of the armour bonuses are kinda high but thats how i like them you can lower if you want and Im not gonna say "DONT LEECH" cuz im posting it its gonna get leeched but if you do use it please put me in credits it didnt take me long to do it but it was frustrating and hard i almost quit many times but anyways heres the dl links for the client and source need client to connect and to see good items oh and specials for stat hammer and vesta long sword work. couldnt figure out how to add auto cast or how to add autocast icon to zuriels staff
Source: http://uppit.com/v/HXMJOYAV Client: http://uppit.com/v/pc9oyc4h

Okay Well Thats All i Really hope you Guys/Girls like it this time i've put alot of effort in to it this time just to impress you guys and a few other people well post if you like/download i dont care if you rep cuz last time all i wanted was rep this time all i want is people to like my work and if you guys like it there will be a V2 prolly devo or delta source or maybe even Czar Cleaned (Tatemo) but not sure yet not gonna work on V2 till i know wether you guys/girls like it or not.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: August 22, 2009, 02:23:22 pm[/size][hr]I Geuss No one Likes it...
